[{"id":"VR813090","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a square loop of wire moving vertically downward out of a magnetic field B, which is directed into the page. Starting on the left vertical side and moving counterclockwise the sides of the square are labeled 1 through 4. Side 1 is two thirds of the way in the field, side 2 is outside of the field, side 3 is two thirds of the way in the field, and side 4 is completely in the field.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR813090.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A square loop of wire is moving at speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v\"><math alttext=\"v\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>v</mi></math></span></span> as it exits a magnetic field directed into the page, as shown. Segments <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3\"><math alttext=\"3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn></math></span></span> of the wire are halfway in the magnetic field, Segment <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> has completely exited the magnetic field, and Segment <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4\"><math alttext=\"4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn></math></span></span> is completely in the magnetic field. Which segment(s) of the loop, if any, will experience a magnetic force from the external magnetic field?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR813090_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">All four segments</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Segments <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3\"><math alttext=\"3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn></math></span></span>, and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4\"><math alttext=\"4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn></math></span></span> only</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Segment <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4\"><math alttext=\"4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn></math></span></span> only</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">None of the segments</p>"],"answer":1}]